{"tid":1162611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有中國民眾為愛國　棄蘋果產品轉用華為手機","createTime":"2019-05-20T03:29:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T09:18:14.000Z","uid":20933,"like":284,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"c1254e4edb66dc123715d579cc947006b1413629","tid":1162611,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T03:29:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20190520_20190520-111352.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20190520_20190520-111352.jpg&h=7f904acf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國政府封殺中國電訊設備製造商華為後，報道指Google亦宣布終止與華為的業務往來，意味華為將來推出新手機，不能再使用Play Store、Gmail等Google服務，但對內地使用者影響不大。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，有民眾表示，由美國蘋果公司推出第一代智能手機開始，一直使用蘋果手機，但一個月前因為支持國貨而轉用華為手機，認為華為手機亦十分好用。他說不清楚華為手機是否有資訊安全問題，只知道作為中國人，就要買國貨。<br />\n<br />\n亦有民眾表示，因為對國貨有信心，因此為家人添置了華為手機，未來亦會繼續支持華為產品。他認為美國政府及Google等的打壓，只會短期影響華為的海外市場，相信華為擁有屬世界前沿的研發團隊及技術，會有較強的抗擊能力。"},{"pid":"49085653900f897a06ec3afef5175b1f39f9ce40","tid":1162611,"uid":20933,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T03:29:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1103652&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1103652%26csid%3D261_341&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ19ey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=204a9c35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1103652&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"c36c2073574df260abc042156aec33a0fddaa03a","tid":1162611,"uid":152476,"like":413,"dislike":1,"score":412,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T03:31:37.000Z","msg":"支那人本來就用唔到google <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7e189367f0122d7d6f8debd21d26492fd6b0295","tid":1162611,"uid":22675,"like":120,"dislike":2,"score":118,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T03:31:48.000Z","msg":"呢個就係要殺曬班中